text: Jayda is a feminine given name, a derivative of Jade via Jada https://ohbabynames.com/all-baby-names/jayda/ or a feminine form of Jayden.https://www.bounty.com/pregnancy-and-birth/baby-names/baby-name- search/j/jayda Notable people named Jayda include: *Jayda Fransen, British politician *Jayda Hylton-Pelaia, Canadian-Jamaican footballer ==References== Category:Feminine given names Category:English feminine given names
